<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a10Jan1939"><font color="red">10 January 1939</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from Richard de la Mere to Paul L&eacute;on): &hellip; I was very glad to hear that Mr Joyce approves the specimen of cloth that I sent him &hellip; I am quite clear about his wishes for the colour of the lettering and I will see that it is light yellow and not gold &hellip; A first proof of the jacket is now being prepared. </div>
